headline: Tesla Stock Slips. This Is What Eclipsed the Robo-Taxi Hype.
summary: Tesla  stock fell Wednesday, as more troubling sales data from Europe rolled in.  Investors remain focused on Tesla’s launch of a robo-taxi business in Austin, Texas.  Wednesday’s drop left Tesla stock up about 2% for the week.
